fields.generated_at: ISO 8601 timestamp when the data was fetched
fields.timeframe: Date range of the data collection period
fields.terms: Dictionary of search terms, each containing:
fields.terms.*.data: Time series of search interest values
fields.terms.*.related_queries: Related search queries for this term
fields.terms.*.metadata: Additional metadata about the term's trends

notes: Contains 138 search terms tracked over the period 2025-01-06 to 2025-12-18 for the US region. Each term includes a timeline of relative search interest (0-100 scale) and related queries. Used by the trends-2025 visualization project.
